Required Features
================================

Module enables specification of a directory on the J-website which file content it lists 
with the appropriate icons

Provides recognition mechanism and icons for:

 - doc / docx - same icon
 - ppt / pps / pptx - same icon
 - xls / xlsx - same icon
 - pdf - same icon
 - avi / mkv / mov / mpg /mpeg / mp4 / flc / swf / wmv - same icon
 - bmp / png / jpg - same icon
 
hosted and publically available at Github to enable future updates